+/*
+ * arcfour.c
+ * by Frank Cusack <frank@google.com>
+ * 100% public domain
+ *
+ * Implemented from the description in _Applied Cryptography_, 2nd ed.
+ *
+ * ** Distribution ** of this software is unlimited and unrestricted.
